Before:

``` js
// Up front
var toString = Object.prototype.toString;

// 21 times thereafter
toString.call(value)
```

After:

``` js
// Up front
var toString = _.bind(Function.call, Object.prototype.toString);

// 21 times thereafter
toString(value)
```

